Text: Please RespondJpst IMAGE IMAGEIMAGE IMAGE Dear Daren iWon really DOES need you and were willing to do just about anything to get your attention even if it means shocking you a little Come back to iWon today Daren and well give you FREE bonus entries Click here After all weve already tried just about everything else new features improved search technology special prizes But this time weve got something that we just know is going to work Think about it it takes most iWon users days and days to rack up that many free chances to win But youll get entries just by clicking on the link below how easy is that IMAGE IMAGE Its a great way to make up for lost time and probably the easiest opportunity youll ever have for chances to win one of this months new prizes plus a chance at our Million Grand Prize So what are you waiting for Come back and check out iWon today Thanks Bill Jonas the iWon Team PS FORGOT YOUR MEMBER NAME It is Jdaren FORGOT YOUR iWON PASSWORD Click here You received this email because when you registered at iWon you agreed to receive email from us To unsubscribe from one or more email categories please click below Please note changes may take up to two weeks to process If youre not signed in you will need to do so before you can update your profile click here You will notice entries have been credited by checking your Monthly and Annual entry counter totals at the top of iWon pages You must be logged in to receive your entries If you click on the link and are not signed in to your iWon account simply sign in and then click on the bonus entry link again Once you are credited with the bonus entries or are determined not to be eligible to receive the entries the link will not work Bonus entries will not allow you to exceed the monthly or annual entry maximum Offer expires
